<div class="text-master">
    <h3 class="m-t-30 semi-bold">Information Collection</h3>
    <p class="fs-16 m-t-20 text-master">
      In order for you to create an account on Hungryhead and use our services, we need to collect and process some of your personal information. Depending on your use of the Services, that may include:
    </p>
    <ul class="fs-16 m-t-20">
      <li class="m-b-10">
        information (such as your name, email and your school, college or university name) that you provide by completing forms on Hungryhead, including if you register as a user of the Services, subscribe to our newsletters, or request any information;
      </li>
      <li class="m-b-10">
        your login and password details, in connection with the account sign-in process;
      </li>
      <li class="m-b-10">
        information about your activity on and interaction with Hungryhead, such as your IP address and the type of device or browser you use;
      </li>
      <li class="m-b-10">
        communications you send to us (for example, when you ask for support, send us questions or comments, or report a problem); and
      </li>
      <li class="m-b-10">
        information that you submit to Hungryhead in the form of comments, feedbacks, investments, questions or messages to other users.
      </li>
    </ul>
</div>


 <div>
    <h3 class="m-t-30 semi-bold">What’s Private</h3>
    <p class="fs-16 m-t-20 text-master">
      This data will not be publicly displayed or revealed to other users:
    </p>
    <ul class="fs-16 m-t-20 text-master">
      <li class="m-b-10">your email</li>
      <li class="m-b-10">your password details</li>
      <li class="m-b-10">your IP address</li>
